<h2 style='margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;'>Learn more about <strong>2048 Game</strong></h2>
<div>
<ul class='unstyled tips-and-tricks'>
<li><a href="/tips-and-tricks">Tips & Tricks</a></li>
